  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2105000/extras/50810e3687478e964d54767447f592ed.poster.avif?t=1686860166\" width=510 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2105000/extras/50810e3687478e964d54767447f592ed.webm?t=1686860166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong><i>Super Choppy Orc</i></strong> is a thrilling 2D precision/puzzle platformer that puts players in the shoes of an Orc on a journey to escape monster-infested caves and rescue his friends.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><br>Master the use of your magical Axe to:<br><strong>Create platforms and reach higher areas</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2105000/extras/39fdf73be682f3548abee82b3b941040.poster.avif?t=1686860166\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2105000/extras/39fdf73be682f3548abee82b3b941040.webm?t=1686860166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2105000/extras/39fdf73be682f3548abee82b3b941040.mp4?t=1686860166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Double jump and get an extra boost of height and distance</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2105000/extras/928a1c43f853914923c22f7cd6a19d8c.poster.avif?t=1686860166\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2105000/extras/928a1c43f853914923c22f7cd6a19d8c.webm?t=1686860166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2105000/extras/928a1c43f853914923c22f7cd6a19d8c.mp4?t=1686860166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Float and gain an extra level of maneuverability</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2105000/extras/3b4dc51eb9113386d90111f031e16f00.poster.avif?t=1686860166\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2105000/extras/3b4dc51eb9113386d90111f031e16f00.webm?t=1686860166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2105000/extras/3b4dc51eb9113386d90111f031e16f00.mp4?t=1686860166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Destroy your enemies and clear a path to victory</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2105000/extras/e12f6780306eb7eb832b19827ef4f750.poster.avif?t=1686860166\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2105000/extras/e12f6780306eb7eb832b19827ef4f750.webm?t=1686860166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2105000/extras/e12f6780306eb7eb832b19827ef4f750.mp4?t=1686860166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br>In addition to its challenging gameplay, the game offers beautiful pixel art and retro-inspired music that transport players back to the golden age of arcade gaming. <br>With its speedrun-friendly design and accessibility options, Super Choppy Orc is a must-play for platformer fans of all skill levels.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Accessibility</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>No use of flashing lights or repeatable patterns, which can be triggering for some players<br></li><li>The ability to highlight different walls with the color of the player's choice, making it easier for colorblind players to navigate the game<br></li><li>Remappable controls, allowing players to customize the controls to their preferences<br></li><li>The ability to slow down the gameplay, making it easier for players with mobility or coordination issues to play the game<br></li><li>The option to become invincible, allowing players to enjoy the game without fear of failure or frustration</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Speedrun</h2><br>Join the  and challenge yourself to become the best at Super Choppy Orc.<br>Can you master the power of the magical Axe and emerge victorious? <br><strong>Play now and find out!</strong>",
